        Hi, I am Hayat, an Interaction Designer with a knack for exploring new
        technologies. Currently pursuing Master of Design at <a
          href="https://www.idc.iitb.ac.in/"
          class="font-bold hover:decoration-black hover:decoration-wavy hover:underline duration-250 transition-all"
